{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"About a year and a half ago,"},{"time":2000,"text":"Stephen Lawler, who also gave a talk"},{"time":5000,"text":"here at TED in 2007 on Virtual Earth,"},{"time":7000,"text":"brought me over to become the architect of Bing Maps,"},{"time":11000,"text":"which is Microsoft's online-mapping effort."},{"time":14000,"text":"In the past two and a half, we've been very hard at work"},{"time":16000,"text":"on redefining the way maps work online."},{"time":20000,"text":"And we really are seeing this in very different terms"},{"time":22000,"text":"from the kind of mapping and direction site"},{"time":24000,"text":"that one is used to."}]},{"cues":[{"time":26000,"text":"So, the first thing that you might notice about the mapping site"},{"time":28000,"text":"is just the fluidity of the zooming and the panning,"},{"time":30000,"text":"which, if you're familiar at all with Seadragon,"},{"time":32000,"text":"that's where it comes from."}]},{"cues":[{"time":34000,"text":"Mapping is, of course,"},{"time":36000,"text":"not just about cartography,"},{"time":38000,"text":"it's also about imagery."},{"time":40000,"text":"So, as we zoom-in beyond a certain level"},{"time":43000,"text":"this resolves into a kind of Sim City-like"},{"time":46000,"text":"virtual view at 45 degrees."},{"time":48000,"text":"This can be viewed from any of the cardinal directions"},{"time":50000,"text":"to show you the 3D structure of the city, all the facades."},{"time":53000,"text":"Now, we see this space, this three-dimensional environment,"},{"time":59000,"text":"as being a canvas on which"},{"time":62000,"text":"all sorts of applications can play out,"},{"time":68000,"text":"and map's directions are really just one of them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":71000,"text":"If you click on this, you'll see"},{"time":74000,"text":"some of the ones that we've put out, just in the past couple of months"},{"time":77000,"text":"since we've launched."},{"time":79000,"text":"So, for example, a couple of days after the disaster in Haiti,"},{"time":81000,"text":"we had an earthquake map that showed"},{"time":83000,"text":"before and after pictures from the sky."},{"time":85000,"text":"This wonderful one which I don't have time to show you"},{"time":87000,"text":"is taking hyper-local blogs in real time"},{"time":90000,"text":"and mapping those stories, those entries"},{"time":92000,"text":"to the places that are referred to on the blogs."},{"time":94000,"text":"It's wonderful."}]},{"cues":[{"time":97000,"text":"But I'm going to show you some more candy sort of stuff."}]},{"cues":[{"time":100000,"text":"So, we see the imagery, of course,"},{"time":104000,"text":"not stopping at the sky."},{"time":107000,"text":"These little green bubbles represent"},{"time":110000,"text":"photosynths that users have made."},{"time":112000,"text":"I'm not going to dive into them either, but photosynths are integrated into the map."},{"time":115000,"text":"Everything that's cased in blue"},{"time":117000,"text":"is an area where we've taken imagery on the ground as well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":122000,"text":"And so, when you fly down --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":124000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":126000,"text":"Thank you. When you fly down to the ground,"},{"time":128000,"text":"and you see this kind of panoramic imagery,"},{"time":131000,"text":"the first thing that you might notice is that it's not just a picture,"},{"time":135000,"text":"there's just as much three-dimensional understanding of this environment"},{"time":138000,"text":"as there is of the three-dimensional city from above,"},{"time":141000,"text":"so if I click on something to get a closer view of it,"},{"time":145000,"text":"then, the fact that that transition looks as it does,"},{"time":148000,"text":"is a function of all of that geometry,"},{"time":150000,"text":"all of that 3D understanding behind this model."}]},{"cues":[{"time":154000,"text":"Now, I'll show you a fun app"},{"time":157000,"text":"that -- we've been working on a collaboration with our friends at Flickr."},{"time":164000,"text":"This takes Flickr, georegistered imagery"},{"time":167000,"text":"and uses photosynth-like processes"},{"time":170000,"text":"to connect that imagery to our imagery, so --"},{"time":174000,"text":"I'm not sure if that's the one I actually meant to pull up, but --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":177000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":180000,"text":"But notice -- this is, of course, a popular tourist site,"},{"time":184000,"text":"and there are lots of photos around here,"},{"time":186000,"text":"and these photos are all taken at different times."},{"time":189000,"text":"So this one was taken around five."},{"time":191000,"text":"So that's the Flickr photo,"},{"time":193000,"text":"that's our imagery."},{"time":195000,"text":"So you really see how this kind of crowd-sourced imagery"},{"time":198000,"text":"is integrating, in a very deep way, into the map itself."}]},{"cues":[{"time":201000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":203000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":205000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":207000,"text":"There are several reasons why this is interesting"},{"time":209000,"text":"and one of them, of course, is time travel."},{"time":211000,"text":"And I'm not going to show you some of the wonderful historic imagery in here,"},{"time":213000,"text":"but there are some with horses and carriages and so on as well."},{"time":216000,"text":"But what's cool about this is that, not only is it augmenting"},{"time":219000,"text":"this visual representation of the world"},{"time":221000,"text":"with things that are coming in from users,"},{"time":224000,"text":"but it also is the foundation for augmented reality,"},{"time":228000,"text":"and that's something that I'll be showing you more of in just a moment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":231000,"text":"Now I just made a transition indoors. That's also interesting."},{"time":235000,"text":"OK, notice there's now a roof above us."},{"time":237000,"text":"We're inside the Pike Place Market."},{"time":240000,"text":"And this is something that we're able to do with a backpack camera,"},{"time":242000,"text":"so, we're now not only imaging in the street"},{"time":246000,"text":"with this camera on tops of cars,"},{"time":248000,"text":"but we're also imaging inside."},{"time":252000,"text":"And from here, we're able to do the same sorts of registration,"},{"time":257000,"text":"not only of still images, but also of video."}]},{"cues":[{"time":261000,"text":"So this is something that we're now going to try"},{"time":263000,"text":"for the first time, live,"},{"time":265000,"text":"and this is really, truly, very frightening."}]},{"cues":[{"time":268000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":271000,"text":"OK."}]},{"cues":[{"time":273000,"text":"(Ringing)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":275000,"text":"All right, guys, are you there?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":277000,"text":"(Noise)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":279000,"text":"All right. I'm hitting it. I'm punching play."},{"time":281000,"text":"I'm live. All right. There we go."},{"time":283000,"text":"So, these are our friends in Pike Place Market, the lab."}]},{"cues":[{"time":288000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":297000,"text":"So they're broadcasting this live."},{"time":299000,"text":"OK, George, can you pan back over to the corner market?"},{"time":303000,"text":"Because I want to show points of interest."},{"time":307000,"text":"No, no. The other way."},{"time":310000,"text":"Yeah, yeah, back to the corner, back to the corner."},{"time":312000,"text":"I don't want to see you guys yet."},{"time":316000,"text":"OK, OK, back to the corner, back to the corner, back to the corner."},{"time":322000,"text":"OK, never mind."}]},{"cues":[{"time":325000,"text":"What I wanted to show you was these points of interest"},{"time":327000,"text":"over here on top of the image"},{"time":329000,"text":"because what that gives you a sense of is the way,"},{"time":331000,"text":"if you're actually on the spot,"},{"time":333000,"text":"you can think about this --"},{"time":335000,"text":"this is taking a step in addition to augmented reality."}]},{"cues":[{"time":338000,"text":"What the hell are you guys -- oh, sorry."}]},{"cues":[{"time":340000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":343000,"text":"We're doing two different --"},{"time":346000,"text":"OK, I'm hanging up now."},{"time":349000,"text":"We're doing two different things here."},{"time":351000,"text":"One of them is to take that real ..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":353000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":360000,"text":"All right, let me just take a moment and thank the team."},{"time":363000,"text":"They've done a fantastic job of pulling this together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":365000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":367000,"text":"I'm going to abandon them now and walk back outside."},{"time":370000,"text":"And while I walk outside, I'll just mention that"},{"time":373000,"text":"here we're using this for telepresence,"},{"time":375000,"text":"but you can equally well use this"},{"time":377000,"text":"on the spot, for augmented reality."},{"time":379000,"text":"When you use it on the spot, it means that"},{"time":381000,"text":"you're able to bring all of that metadata"},{"time":383000,"text":"and information about the world to you."},{"time":385000,"text":"So here, we're taking the extra step of also broadcasting it."},{"time":387000,"text":"That was being broadcast, by the way, on a 4G network"},{"time":390000,"text":"from the market."}]},{"cues":[{"time":393000,"text":"All right, and now there's one last TED talk"},{"time":396000,"text":"that Microsoft has given in the past several years."},{"time":398000,"text":"And that's Curtis Wong, WorldWide Telescope."},{"time":401000,"text":"So, we're going to head over to the dumpsters,"},{"time":403000,"text":"where it's traditional, after a long day at the market,"},{"time":406000,"text":"to go out for a break, but also stare up at the sky."},{"time":410000,"text":"This is the integration"},{"time":412000,"text":"of WorldWide Telescope into our maps."}]},{"cues":[{"time":415000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":417000,"text":"This is the current -- thank you --"},{"time":420000,"text":"this is the current time. If we scrub the time,"},{"time":422000,"text":"then we can see how the sky will look at different times,"},{"time":425000,"text":"and we can get all of this very detailed"},{"time":427000,"text":"information about different times, different dates:"},{"time":432000,"text":"Let's move the moon a little higher in the sky,"},{"time":434000,"text":"maybe change the date."},{"time":438000,"text":"I would like to kind of zoom in on the moon."},{"time":444000,"text":"So, this is an astronomically complete"},{"time":446000,"text":"representation of the sky"},{"time":449000,"text":"integrated right into the Earth."}]},{"cues":[{"time":451000,"text":"All right now, I've overrun my time,"},{"time":453000,"text":"so I've got to stop."},{"time":455000,"text":"Thank you all very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":457000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}